snippet.title: HBO Max
snippet.description: HBO Max is the premium streaming platform that bundles together all of HBO with even more of your favorite movies and TV shows from Warner Bros. Discovery, New Line, DC, CNN, TNT, TBS, truTV, Turner Classic Movies, Cartoon Network, Adult Swim, Crunchyroll, Rooster Teeth, Looney Tunes, and much more. Enjoy all of this, plus an exciting lineup of new original programming with Max Originals, all in one place.
